rows.label: qst400201_msg0002
rows.name:
But Turuni is informant by trade.
Can not provide information without
proper compensation.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0004
rows.name:
Inside Divine Beast battleship, Gulan girl
being held prisoner.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0005
rows.name:
Unfortunately Turuni not yet receive
intelligence specifying prisoner name.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0006
rows.name:
But rumor say, big ship arrive for sole
purpose of holding one measly girl.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0007
rows.name:
People of Gula getting along quite
well with Empire nowadays, so trouble
like this not very welcome!

rows.label: qst400201_msg0008
rows.name:
That seem to be opinion of
most of Trigo resident.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0009
rows.name:
That about extent of information
Turuni know.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0011
rows.name:
Turuni offer super-special bargain
price and friends still not purchase?

rows.label: qst400201_msg0012
rows.name:
If friends short on cash, maybe should
go outside town and defeat monster.

rows.label: qst400201_msg0013
rows.name:
Normally, Turuni charge for this
kind of information too, but this time
provide specially for free.
